description:
ScifiPunks is a limited edition collection of 451 iconic sci-fi characters immortalized in punk form on the Ethereum blockchain. Each 1/1 edition is hand-generated by [@patternbase](https://opensea.io/accounts/Patternbase). 

Follow @ScifiPunks on [Discord](https://discord.gg/4TZYFNBjwq) | [Twitter](http://www.twitter.com/scifipunks) | [Instagram](http://www.instagram.com/scifipunks) | [Website](http://www.scifipunks.com)

[ScifiPunks](https://opensea.io/collection/scifipunks) is a certified subgenre of  [Unofficial Punks™](https://opensea.io/assets?search[sortAscending]=false&search[sortBy]=CREATED_DATE&search[stringTraits][0][name]=Certified&search[stringTraits][0][values][0]=Unofficial%20Punks).  
Only 451 ScifiPunks will ever be released.

⚠️ This project pays homage to the OG cryptopunks project and is not affiliated with Larva Labs.
